						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone built into the wall of the temple of Paramēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>Vikramāditya VI—A.D. 1120.</p>						

						<p>This hero-stone dated in the <hi rend="bold">[Chālukya]-Vikrama year 45, Śārvari, Vaiśākha s11u. 5, Sunday,</hi> commemorates the death of <hi rend="bold">Eḍava Bamma,</hi> who fought for his master <hi rend="bold">Eṟakagāvuḍa.</hi> The details of the date correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1120, April 4, Sunday, f.d.t. ·10</hi></p>						

